- Create a Jenkins node

Create an instance in a cloud provider

Use the wget command to get the agent.jar
http://178.128.38.40:8080/jnlpJars/agent.jar

Then, Run from agent command line from the node create on Jenkins (Example):
java -jar agent.jar -jnlpUrl http://IP:PORT/computer/builder2/slave-agent.jnlp -secret
secret -workDir "/var/jenkins/"


